<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: #0d6efd;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f1f1f1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Kloners Stock ISMS</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you onboard!</p>

      <p>You now have access to our Inventory & Stock Management System.</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Track and manage your stock</li>
        <li>Get insights and analytics</li>
        <li>Stay updated with stock alerts</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Login to your account and start exploring:</p>
      <p><a href="{{Date}}" target="_blank">{{appUrl}}</a></p>

      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>

      <p>Regards,<br />The Kloners Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{count}} Kloners ISMS. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
